text: Avtandil Jorbenadze (23 February 1951 - 17 May 2024) was a Georgian doctor, politician, and former State Minister of Georgia. He was minister before the Rose Revolution in Georgia. He also held the position of health minister. Jorbenadze died on 17 May 2024 at the age of 73.ავთანდილ ჯორბენაძე 73 წლის ასაკში გარდაიცვალა ==References== ==More reading== *East, R. and Thomas, R.
